WEBVTT

00:07.150 --> 00:10.150
<b><b>《权力的游戏》前情提要</b></b>

00:12.170 --> 00:13.920
我们已经打赢了生死之战
We have won the Great War.

00:15.040 --> 00:16.500
现在我们要赢下最后一战
Now we will win the last war.

00:16.870 --> 00:19.000
我们的目标是在不摧毁君临的前提下
The objective here is to remove Cersei

00:19.080 --> 00:20.960
除掉瑟曦
without destroying King's Landing.

00:23.290 --> 00:24.920
你打算去君临？
You heading to King's Landing?

00:25.120 --> 00:26.960
我还有些事没有做了断
There's some unfinished business.

00:27.250 --> 00:28.170
我也是
Me too.

00:28.420 --> 00:30.250
我没准备回来
I don't plan on coming back.

00:31.080 --> 00:32.420
我也是
Neither do I.

00:34.040 --> 00:37.290
我一直希望着能亲眼目睹他们处决你姐姐
I always wanted to be there when they execute your sister.

00:38.250 --> 00:39.920
看来我没这个机会了
Seems like I won't get the chance.

00:41.170 --> 00:42.710
留在我身边
Stay with me.

00:43.920 --> 00:45.080
求你了
Please.

00:45.500 --> 00:46.920
瑟曦面目可憎
Cersei's hateful...

00:49.420 --> 00:50.460
我又何尝不是
And so am I.

00:59.330 --> 01:00.790
我要告诉你们一件事
I need to tell you something.

01:03.290 --> 01:06.250
但是你们得发誓不会告诉任何人
But you have to swear you'll never tell another soul.

01:06.330 --> 01:09.420
如果还有其他人呢？其他更好的人选？
What if there's someone else? Someone better.

01:09.870 --> 01:12.620
在某个时刻 你会选择一个你信赖的人
At a certain point, you choose a person you believe in,

01:12.710 --> 01:14.040
为那人战斗
and you fight for that person.

01:14.120 --> 01:16.330
即便你知道这是个错误的选择？
Even if you know it's a mistake?

01:19.120 --> 01:20.950
他的继承顺位更靠前
He has the better claim to the throne.

01:20.950 --> 01:22.350
每个坦格利安诞生之时
Every time a Targaryen is born,

01:22.350 --> 01:23.570
诸神都会抛一枚硬币
the gods flip a coin.

01:23.570 --> 01:25.610
疯王处决了他的敌人
The Mad King gave his enemies the justice

01:25.610 --> 01:26.720
他认为他们罪有应得
he thought they deserved.

01:26.720 --> 01:27.940
子女和父辈并不一样
Children are not their fathers.

01:27.940 --> 01:30.050
- 成为一条巨龙吧  - 您有颗仁慈的心
- Be a dragon. - You have a gentle heart.

01:30.050 --> 01:32.540
一个坦格利安族人孤独地活在世上
A Targaryen alone in the world

01:32.540 --> 01:34.010
是件很可悲的事情
is a terrible thing.

01:34.010 --> 01:35.900
你不想唤醒睡龙之怒 对吧？
You don't want to awake the dragon, do you?

