03:48.790 --> 03:51.660
<b>瓦里斯
</b>“八爪蜘蛛”

04:05.290 --> 04:06.210
请进
Come in.

04:10.210 --> 04:11.330
说呀？
And?

04:13.120 --> 04:14.670
没效果么？
Nothing?

04:14.750 --> 04:16.370
她没吃
She won't eat.

04:21.250 --> 04:23.460
我们晚餐时再试试吧
We'll try again at supper.

04:25.710 --> 04:27.370
我觉得他们在盯着我
I think they're watching me.

04:28.370 --> 04:32.290
- 谁？ - 她的士兵
- Who? - Her soldiers.

04:32.370 --> 04:36.330
当然了 那是他们的职责
Of course they are. That's their job.

04:46.500 --> 04:48.290
玛莎 我和你说过什么来着
What have I told you, Martha?

04:49.620 --> 04:52.830
风险越大 回报越大
The greater the risk, the greater the reward.

04:54.170 --> 04:57.040
去吧 厨房那边找不到你会起疑的
Go on. They'll be missing you in the kitchen.

05:08.990 --> 05:12.370
<b>提利昂·兰尼斯特
</b>“小恶魔” 丹妮莉丝的女王之手

05:20.580 --> 05:22.210
北境军队呢？
The Northern armies?

05:22.290 --> 05:23.790
刚刚渡过三叉戟河
Just crossed the Trident.

05:23.870 --> 05:26.750
他们大概两天后到达君临城外
They'll be at the walls of King's Landing in two days.

05:27.920 --> 05:29.420
她情况如何？
How is she?

05:29.500 --> 05:32.120
自打我们回来之后她就没见过任何人
She hasn't seen anyone since we returned.

05:32.210 --> 05:35.540
房门不出 水米未进
Hasn't left her chambers, hasn't accepted any food.

05:36.710 --> 05:38.460
她不该一个人呆着
She shouldn't be alone.

05:38.540 --> 05:41.620
你为她担忧 我敬佩你的怜悯之心
You're worried for her. I admire your empathy.

05:41.710 --> 05:43.580
你难道不担心么？
Aren't you worried for her?

05:43.670 --> 05:45.790
我担心的是我们所有人
I'm worried for all of us.

05:45.870 --> 05:48.040
人们常说每个坦格利安诞生之时
They say every time a Targaryen is born,

05:48.120 --> 05:51.330
诸神就会抛一枚硬币 而整个世界都会屏息以待
the gods toss a coin and the world holds its breath.

05:51.420 --> 05:54.170
我们北方人可不爱玩猜谜
We're not much for riddles where I'm from.

05:54.250 --> 05:57.080
你我都明白她会采取什么行动
We both know what she's about to do.

06:00.290 --> 06:03.460
<b>琼恩·雪诺 
</b>伊耿·坦格利安 铁王座法理继承人

06:02.960 --> 06:05.310
那是她该做的决定 她是我们的女王
That's her decision to make. She is our queen.

06:05.310 --> 06:09.290
权力取决于人心 不管人们是否意识到这一点
Men decide where power resides, whether or not they know it.

06:11.830 --> 06:13.620
你到底想要什么？
What do you want?

06:13.710 --> 06:15.460
我想要的从未改变过
All I've ever wanted.

06:15.540 --> 06:18.460
让一个真正合适的统治者坐上铁王座
The right ruler on the Iron Throne.

06:20.000 --> 06:22.830
她那枚硬币会哪面朝上我不得而知
I still don't know how her coin has landed.

06:22.920 --> 06:26.250
但你那枚我已经很清楚了
But I'm quite certain about yours.

06:34.290 --> 06:36.210
我不想要这个王位
I don't want it.

06:36.290 --> 06:37.620
从没想过
I never have.

06:40.080 --> 06:43.790
我见识过的国王和女王比这世上任何人都要多
I have known more kings and queens than any man living.

06:43.870 --> 06:45.540
我听过他们对老百姓说的好话
I've heard what they say to crowds,

06:45.540 --> 06:47.460
也见过他们背地里干的勾当
and seen what they do in the shadows.

06:47.540 --> 06:50.920
我也曾帮助他们实现计划 无论那有多可怕
I have furthered their designs, however horrible.

06:51.000 --> 06:53.710
但现在我对你说的句句属实
But what I tell you now is true:

06:53.790 --> 06:57.000
你可以做到政治清明 而她——
You will rule wisely and well, while she--

06:57.080 --> 06:58.870
她是……
She...

06:58.960 --> 07:00.040
我的女王
is my queen.

07:21.870 --> 07:23.330
陛下
Your Grace?

07:48.540 --> 07:51.000
有件事需要禀报您
There's something you need to know.

07:51.280 --> 07:54.160
<b>丹妮莉丝·坦格利安
</b>“风暴降生”“龙之母”

07:52.290 --> 07:54.540
有人背叛了我
Someone has betrayed me.

08:00.710 --> 08:02.080
是的
Yes.

08:06.040 --> 08:07.830
琼恩·雪诺
Jon Snow.

08:13.710 --> 08:14.670
瓦里斯
Varys.

08:16.870 --> 08:19.000
他知道了琼恩的真实出身
He knows the truth about Jon.

08:20.290 --> 08:21.830
是的
He does.

08:26.580 --> 08:28.920
因为你告诉了他
Because you told him.

08:31.210 --> 08:32.960
珊莎透露给你
You learned from Sansa.

08:33.920 --> 08:35.580
而她又是从琼恩口中得知的
And she learned from Jon,

08:35.670 --> 08:38.250
尽管我求过他不要告诉珊莎
though I begged him not to tell her.

08:39.620 --> 08:41.460
所以我说……
As I said...

08:42.210 --> 08:43.290
他背叛了我
he betrayed me.

08:43.370 --> 08:45.210
我很庆幸珊莎告知了我
I'm glad Sansa told me.

08:45.290 --> 08:46.830
我是您的首相啊
I am your Hand.

08:46.920 --> 08:49.420
您所要面对的所有威胁我都应该知晓
I need to be aware of any threats you're facing.

08:50.920 --> 08:52.210
那瓦里斯呢？
And Varys?

08:52.290 --> 08:55.420
您的情报总管也应当知晓
Your Master of Whisperers needs to be aware too.

08:56.250 --> 08:58.670
但你先告诉了他
You spoke to him first.

08:58.750 --> 09:00.000
没有提前向我请示
Without coming to me.

09:00.080 --> 09:02.540
没有经过我的允许
Without asking my permission.

09:04.170 --> 09:06.790
这是我的失误
It was a mistake.

09:08.790 --> 09:11.580
你以为珊莎为什么要透露给你？
Why do you think Sansa told you?

09:11.670 --> 09:13.420
你以为她想得到什么结果？
What do you think she hoped to gain?

09:13.460 --> 09:17.080
- 她信任我  - 她当然信任你
- She trusts me. - Yes, she trusts you.

09:18.210 --> 09:22.290
她相信你一定会把秘密传播出去
She trusted you to spread secrets

09:22.370 --> 09:25.460
这个秘密足以毁了你的女王
that could destroy your own queen.

09:27.460 --> 09:29.750
你显然没让她失望
And you did not let her down.

09:33.420 --> 09:36.960
我的女王 如果我辜负了您 原谅我
If I have failed you, my queen, forgive me.

09:38.830 --> 09:41.120
但我们是出于好意
Our intentions were good.

09:42.540 --> 09:46.120
我们的目标和您一致 那就是创造一个更美好的世界
We wanted what you want. A better world, all of us.

09:47.370 --> 09:50.210
瓦里斯也是如此
Varys as much as anyone.

09:58.920 --> 10:01.040
但现在这都不重要了
But it doesn't matter now.

10:03.210 --> 10:04.170
没错
No.

10:05.500 --> 10:07.170
现在不重要了
It doesn't matter now.

11:04.140 --> 11:06.430
<b>灰虫子
</b>无垢者指挥官

12:07.620 --> 12:09.580
是我告发的
It was me.

12:14.960 --> 12:16.580
我希望这是我罪有应得
I hope I deserve this.

12:16.670 --> 12:18.330
真的
Truly, I do.

12:18.420 --> 12:20.500
我希望是我错了
I hope I'm wrong.

12:28.040 --> 12:29.120
再见了 老朋友
Goodbye, old friend.

13:10.620 --> 13:11.710
瓦里斯大人
Lord Varys.

13:13.460 --> 13:15.620
我 坦格利安家族的
I, Daenerys of House Targaryen,

13:15.710 --> 13:17.540
丹妮莉丝一世
First of My Name,

13:17.620 --> 13:20.870
打碎镣铐之人 龙之母
Breaker of Chains and Mother of Dragons...

13:22.710 --> 13:24.750
宣判你死刑
sentence you to die.

13:23.780 --> 13:26.450
<b>卓耿
</b>丹妮莉丝的黑龙

13:35.250 --> 13:36.370
龙焰
Dracarys.

14:27.540 --> 14:29.090
这是我们跨过狭海时
This was all she brought with her

14:29.090 --> 14:31.120
她带来的全部东西
when we crossed the Narrow Sea.

14:32.210 --> 14:34.250
她唯一的财产
Her only possession.

15:18.890 --> 15:21.240
没事的 灰虫子

15:21.240 --> 15:23.940
让我跟他说几句话

15:49.960 --> 15:52.580
我说过如果你告诉你妹妹 会发生什么来着？
What did I say would happen if you told your sister?

15:52.670 --> 15:55.960
我不想要铁王座 我告诉过瓦里斯了
I don't want it, and that's what I told him.

15:57.250 --> 15:59.460
你妹妹背叛了你的信任
She betrayed your trust.

15:59.540 --> 16:01.290
瓦里斯的死 她也有责任
She killed Varys as much as I did.

16:02.920 --> 16:05.370
这对她来说是一场胜利
This was a victory for her.

16:06.870 --> 16:08.280
现在她明白 
Now she knows what happens

16:08.280 --> 16:10.080
当人们知道你的身世后 会发生什么了
when people hear the truth about you.

16:12.710 --> 16:16.710
维斯特洛的人民爱你远胜过我
Far more people in Westeros love you than love me.

16:19.210 --> 16:21.580
这里没人爱戴我
I don't have love here.

16:23.040 --> 16:25.080
他们只是怕我
I only have fear.

16:28.000 --> 16:29.870
你有我啊
I love you.

16:32.420 --> 16:35.210
你永远都是我的女王
And you will always be my queen.

16:42.040 --> 16:44.040
我对你而言只是如此吗？
Is that all I am to you?

16:45.790 --> 16:47.750
仅仅是你的女王？
Your queen?

17:24.620 --> 17:26.580
好吧
All right, then.

17:33.960 --> 17:35.790
那就怕下去吧
Let it be fear.

17:39.790 --> 17:43.040
生活在这里的百姓不是你的敌人
The people who live there, they're not your enemies.

17:43.330 --> 17:46.240
他们是无辜的 就像你在弥林解放的那些奴隶一样
They're innocents, like the ones you liberated in Meereen.

17:46.250 --> 17:48.220
在我到弥林的时候
In Meereen, the slaves turned on the masters

17:48.220 --> 17:51.040
奴隶们就已经奋起反抗并且解放了城市
and liberated the city themselves the moment I arrived.

17:51.120 --> 17:52.330
但君临百姓还在害怕
They're afraid.

17:52.420 --> 17:53.740
任何反抗瑟曦的人
Anyone who resists Cersei

17:53.750 --> 17:55.870
他的家族都会被株连
will see his family butchered.

17:55.960 --> 17:58.170
你不能指望他们充英雄
You can't expect them to be heroes.

17:58.250 --> 18:00.370
- 他们是人质 - 是啊
- They're hostages. - They are.

18:00.460 --> 18:03.790
他们被暴君挟持是谁的错？是我的错吗？
In a tyrant's grip. Whose fault is that? Mine?

18:03.870 --> 18:06.500
是谁的错又有什么关系呢？
What does it matter whose fault it is?

18:06.580 --> 18:09.460
如果城市被焚毁 成千上万的孩子都会死去
Thousands of children will die if the city burns.

18:09.540 --> 18:10.790
你姐姐很清楚
Your sister knows how to use

18:10.870 --> 18:12.920
如何利用敌人的弱点去对抗他们
her enemies' weaknesses against them.

18:13.000 --> 18:15.420
她认为我们的仁慈就是
That's what she thinks our mercy is:

18:15.500 --> 18:16.670
我们的弱点
weakness.

18:16.750 --> 18:18.830
- 我恳求您 我的女王 - 但是她错了
- I beg you, my queen - But she's wrong.

18:19.710 --> 18:21.500
仁慈是我们的优势
Mercy is our strength.

18:22.750 --> 18:25.120
但我们的仁慈是留给后世百姓的
Our mercy towards future generations

18:25.210 --> 18:27.790
他们将永远不会再被暴君挟持为人质
who will never again be held hostage by a tyrant.

18:33.750 --> 18:35.370
召集无垢者
Ready the Unsullied.

18:35.460 --> 18:37.280
今晚你们就乘船前往君临
Tonight you sail for King's Landing

18:37.280 --> 18:39.080
- 加入北境大军 - 如果瑟曦的追随者们
- to join the Northern armies. - Cersei's followers

18:39.080 --> 18:41.080
知道这一仗赢不了的话 他们会抛弃她的
will abandon her if they know the war is lost.

18:41.080 --> 18:42.540
给他们这个机会
Give them that chance.

18:43.490 --> 18:45.090
如果他们投降了
If the city surrenders,

18:45.090 --> 18:46.700
他们会鸣钟并且打开城门
they will ring the bells and raise the gates.

18:46.710 --> 18:50.370
如果您听到了钟声 求您下令停止进攻
Please, if you hear them ringing the bells, call off the attack.

18:58.540 --> 19:00.540
在城外等着我
Wait for me outside the city.

19:01.620 --> 19:03.330
到时候你会知道怎么办的
You'll know when it's time.

19:32.870 --> 19:36.750
你哥哥想要穿越防线 被我们抓住了
Your brother was stopped trying to get past our lines.

19:41.080 --> 19:44.580
看来他到最后也没有抛弃你的姐姐
It seems he hasn't abandoned your sister after all.

19:50.290 --> 19:51.920
下一次你再辜负我对你的信任……
The next time you fail me...

19:53.290 --> 19:55.750
我就不会再给你机会了
will be the last time you fail me.

20:12.540 --> 20:14.540
让他们过去
Let them pass.

20:25.960 --> 20:27.540
穿过大门
Through the gate.

21:10.540 --> 21:13.460
后卫部队天亮前应该就会到达
The rearguard should be here by daybreak.

21:13.540 --> 21:16.000
她想要现在就攻城
She wants to attack now.

21:14.080 --> 21:17.080
<b>戴佛斯·席渥斯
</b>“洋葱骑士”

21:17.210 --> 21:18.670
最早也得等到天亮
Daybreak at the earliest.

21:25.790 --> 21:27.000
戴佛斯
Davos.

21:29.580 --> 21:31.870
你得帮我个忙
I need to ask you a favor.

21:34.000 --> 21:36.500
你是这世上最牛逼的走私犯 对吧？
You're the greatest smuggler alive, aren't you?

21:38.040 --> 21:41.420
这个忙不太好帮是么？
I'm not gonna like this favor, am I?

21:51.960 --> 21:54.830
等下 你们要去哪里？
Ay up. Where you going?

21:56.000 --> 21:59.580
<b>桑铎·克里冈
</b>“猎狗”

21:56.000 --> 21:59.580
<b>艾莉亚·史塔克</b>

21:56.250 --> 21:58.250
我是艾莉亚·史塔克
I'm Arya Stark.

21:58.330 --> 22:00.870
我要去杀瑟曦女王
I'm going to kill Queen Cersei.

22:05.370 --> 22:06.370
想想看
Think about it.

22:06.460 --> 22:09.080
要是她杀了瑟曦 战争也就结束了
She kills Cersei, the war's over.

22:09.170 --> 22:12.540
围城战不用打了 明天你也许就不至于战死
There won't be a siege.You might not even die tomorrow.

22:15.830 --> 22:17.670
我需要向长官通报
I need to go talk to my captain.

22:17.750 --> 22:19.750
去啊 向他通报
Go ahead, talk to him.

22:22.500 --> 22:24.210
他要去哪？
Where's he going?

22:38.180 --> 22:41.750
我喝吃头骨看守

22:43.200 --> 22:47.120
我想吃头骨看守

22:50.550 --> 22:54.300
我想见……

22:54.330 --> 22:55.920
我们会说通用语
We speak the common tongue.

22:56.920 --> 22:58.830
啊 那就好
Ah. Good.

22:58.920 --> 23:00.670
我想和囚犯单独呆着
I want to be alone with the prisoner.

23:00.750 --> 23:02.920
休息一会吧 明天会很漫长
Get some rest. Tomorrow will be a long day.

23:03.000 --> 23:05.370
我们有令在身 要看守囚犯
We have orders to guard the prisoner.

23:05.460 --> 23:07.250
谁下令的？ 女王吗？
Ordered by whom? The queen herself?

23:08.460 --> 23:10.730
- 不是 - 这样的话
- No. - Well, in that case,

23:10.730 --> 23:13.460
作为女王之手 我可比下这命令的人级别高
as Hand of the Queen, I outrank whomever gave your order.

23:13.540 --> 23:15.080
可能高很多
Probably by quite a lot.

23:32.010 --> 23:35.010
<b>詹姆·兰尼斯特
</b>“弑君者”

23:38.790 --> 23:40.790
他们怎么发现你的？
How did they find you?

23:48.960 --> 23:51.370
你没考虑过把它取下来吗？
Did you consider taking it off?

23:52.830 --> 23:56.290
瑟曦曾叫我 “最蠢的兰尼斯特”
Cersei once called me "the stupidest Lannister."

23:57.790 --> 24:01.040
你要回到她身边 陪她去送死
And you're going back to her, to die with her.

24:02.210 --> 24:03.830
你之前低估她了
You've underestimated her before.

24:03.840 --> 24:05.390
她死定了
She's going to die.

24:06.460 --> 24:07.960
除非你能说服她
Unless you can convince her

24:07.960 --> 24:09.580
让她改变一下作战方针
to change her course of action.

24:09.670 --> 24:11.670
在这儿很难做到
Difficult to do from here.

24:17.290 --> 24:20.420
我哪次动摇过她的想法？
When have I ever been able to convince Cersei of anything?

24:20.500 --> 24:22.080
那就尽量
Try.

24:22.170 --> 24:24.190
就算不为你自己 不为她
If not for yourself, if not for her,

24:24.520 --> 24:27.080
也要为君临城的众多百姓努力
then for every one of the million people in that city,

24:27.080 --> 24:28.560
无论这些人是否无辜
innocent or otherwise.

24:28.560 --> 24:31.460
说实话 我从来没有真正在乎过他们
To be honest, I never really cared much for them.

24:31.540 --> 24:33.370
无论这些人是否无辜
Innocent or otherwise.

24:34.540 --> 24:36.670
有一个无辜者你肯定在乎
You do care for one innocent.

24:37.580 --> 24:39.080
我知道你一定会
I know you do.

24:39.170 --> 24:40.920
瑟曦也会
And so does Cersei.

24:42.210 --> 24:43.920
她现在有理由这么做
She has a reason now.

24:45.370 --> 24:49.120
那个孩子就是她寸步不让的理由
The child is the reason she'll never give an inch.

24:49.210 --> 24:51.000
她做过那么多可怕的事情
All the worst things she's ever done,

24:51.080 --> 24:53.460
都是为了她的孩子
she's done for her children.

24:53.540 --> 24:55.710
她也不是完全不可能打赢
It's not impossible that she'll win.

24:55.790 --> 24:57.000
她不会赢的
She won't.

24:57.080 --> 24:59.090
她的敌人的兵力都已损耗大半
Her enemy's forces have been depleted,

24:59.090 --> 25:00.650
正如她所说的那样
as she said they would be.

25:00.650 --> 25:02.750
三条龙中的两条已经死了
Two of the three dragons are dead.

25:02.830 --> 25:05.680
- 她已经扳回了劣势 - 君临明天一定会陷落
- She's evened the odds. - The city will fall tomorrow.

25:05.690 --> 25:07.520
她有兰尼斯特大军 她有黄金团——
She has the Lannister army, she has the Golden Company--

25:07.530 --> 25:09.530
上次君临遭到攻击时 是我在保卫它
I defended the city last time it was attacked.

25:09.530 --> 25:11.710
我比任何人都清楚 明天它会陷落
I know it better than anyone. It will fall tomorrow.

25:11.710 --> 25:14.300
那看来我要死在明天了 除非我还会死得更早
Then I suppose I'll die tomorrow, if not before.

25:14.310 --> 25:15.920
为什么？
Why?

25:22.120 --> 25:23.620
逃吧
Escape.

25:23.710 --> 25:25.710
你们俩一起
The two of you, together.

25:25.790 --> 25:27.360
记得我们曾经会面的地方吗
Remember where we met,

25:27.390 --> 25:29.000
在红堡地下
where they keep the dragon skulls,

25:29.000 --> 25:30.180
存放龙头骨的地方？
beneath the Red Keep?

25:31.580 --> 25:32.870
把她带到那里去
Take her down there.

25:32.960 --> 25:34.730
沿着楼梯一直往下走
Keep following the stairways down,

25:34.730 --> 25:36.050
走到最深处
down as far as they'll go.

25:36.060 --> 25:38.500
你们就能出来 到红堡脚下的沙滩上
You'll come out onto a beach at the foot of the keep.

25:38.580 --> 25:40.540
那儿会有只小船等着你们
A dinghy will be waiting for you.

25:41.750 --> 25:43.120
划出海湾
Sail out of the bay.

25:43.210 --> 25:45.920
如果风向合适 你们就能划到潘托斯
If the winds are kind, you'll make it to Pentos.

25:47.080 --> 25:49.500
开始新的生活吧
Start a new life.

25:52.830 --> 25:56.170
从铁舰队眼皮底下划船过去 开始新生活？
Sail right past the Iron Fleet and into a new life?

25:56.250 --> 25:58.920
听起来比瑟曦打胜仗更不靠谱
Sounds a lot less likely than Cersei winning this war--

25:59.000 --> 26:01.620
很快那里就不会有什么铁舰队了
There won't be an Iron Fleet for much longer.

26:02.830 --> 26:04.080
去吧
Do it.

26:04.170 --> 26:07.290
如果你不这么做 你永远都见不到瑟曦了
If you don't, you'll never see Cersei again.

26:13.170 --> 26:14.960
对我发誓
Swear to me.

26:18.250 --> 26:20.170
我保证
You have my word.

26:24.790 --> 26:26.210
如果成功了
If it works,

26:26.290 --> 26:28.260
就下令敲响君临所有的钟
give the order to ring all the bells

26:28.260 --> 26:30.330
打开城门
in King's Landing and open the gates.

26:30.330 --> 26:32.720
这会是君临城投降的信号
That will be our signal that the city has surrendered.

26:32.730 --> 26:34.210
我会尽力
I'll try.

26:35.620 --> 26:38.000
我从没想过 我会报答你的帮助
I never thought I'd get to repay the favor.

26:38.080 --> 26:41.000
记住 敲钟 开城门
Remember, ring the bells and open the gates.

26:41.000 --> 26:43.320
你的女王会因此处决你的
Your queen will execute you for this.

26:43.330 --> 26:45.180
如果丹妮莉丝可以不用大开杀戒
If Daenerys can make it to the throne

26:45.180 --> 26:47.330
就登上王位
without wading through a river of blood,

26:47.420 --> 26:48.570
或许她就会仁慈地对待
maybe she'll show mercy

26:48.580 --> 26:50.830
帮她实现这一切的人
to the person who made that possible.

26:56.580 --> 26:59.330
成千上万的无辜百姓......
Tens of thousands of innocent lives...

27:00.620 --> 27:03.830
和一个不是那么无辜的侏儒……
one not particularly innocent dwarf...

27:05.250 --> 27:07.830
这波交易不亏
it seems like a fair trade.

27:14.370 --> 27:16.370
如果不是你
If it weren't for you,

27:16.460 --> 27:18.620
我早就夭折了
I never would've survived my childhood.

27:20.750 --> 27:22.580
才不会
You would have.

27:30.210 --> 27:31.750
你是唯一一个
You were the only one

27:32.960 --> 27:35.870
没有把我当成怪物的人
who didn't treat me like a monster.

27:38.460 --> 27:40.710
你是我的全部
You were all I had.

28:45.950 --> 28:49.080
<b>攸伦·葛雷乔伊
</b>铁群岛之王

28:51.580 --> 28:54.000
注意地平线！
Eyes on the horizon!

28:55.290 --> 28:57.290
蝎弩装弹！
Load the scorpion!

29:10.540 --> 29:11.960
弓箭手 跟上！
Archers, close up!

29:12.040 --> 29:13.420
过来！
Come on!

29:13.500 --> 29:15.500
弹射弩就位！
Up to the espringal!

29:15.580 --> 29:17.790
到它后面去！
To the back of it!

29:29.750 --> 29:31.460
弓箭手 列队！
Archers, line up!

29:39.500 --> 29:41.000
这边！过来！
This way! Come on!

29:41.080 --> 29:42.670
现在清理街道！
Clear the streets now!

29:42.750 --> 29:45.000
- 不！ - 赶快进去！
- No! - In, now.

29:45.080 --> 29:47.750
- 你 过来 - 赶紧回屋！
- And you, come on. - Inside, now!

29:47.830 --> 29:49.250
快点
Quickly.

29:49.330 --> 29:50.420
是的 朝那边走
Yes. Follow down there.

29:50.500 --> 29:52.290
他们来了 到红堡去
They're here. Get to the Red Keep.

29:54.000 --> 29:55.960
- 儿子！ - 进去！
- My son! - Get inside!

30:00.290 --> 30:02.210
就在你前面 我看见了！
Just ahead of you, I can see it!

30:02.290 --> 30:03.620
好吧 行动！
All right, move it!

30:03.710 --> 30:05.540
- 过来！ - 往前走！
- Come on! - Keep moving!

30:05.620 --> 30:07.290
- 往前走！- 继续往前！
- Keep going! - Keep moving!

30:07.370 --> 30:09.120
- 快点！ - 一直往前！
- Quickly! - All the way!

30:09.210 --> 30:11.120
- 过来！ - 过来！
- Come on! - Come on!

30:11.210 --> 30:13.330
抓紧你妈妈的手！
Hold your mother's hand!

30:26.080 --> 30:30.000
给黄金团让路！
Make way for the Golden Company!

30:39.040 --> 30:40.290
关上大门！
Close the gate!

31:12.000 --> 31:15.220
<b>哈利·斯崔克兰
</b>黄金团团长

31:44.750 --> 31:47.790
如果你听到了钟声 就表示他们投降了
If you hear the bells ring, they've surrendered.

31:47.870 --> 31:49.790
让你手下的人停手
Call off your men.

32:02.120 --> 32:04.370
兄弟 向前走
Move along now, lads.

32:21.410 --> 32:24.250
<b>瑟曦·兰尼斯特
</b>铁王座上的女王

32:33.120 --> 32:35.710
- 就这样 - 继续 快走
- That's it. - Go on, move it.

32:38.960 --> 32:42.210
跟上 动起来 走起来 快点 快一点 跟上 快走
Come on, move, move. Faster, faster. Come on, move it.

32:42.290 --> 32:44.120
- 继续走 - 继续向前走
- Keep going. - Keep moving.

32:47.960 --> 32:50.330
- 让开 - 别和他走散了
- Move. - Stay with him.

32:51.540 --> 32:53.120
- 抓好了 - 抓住我的手
- Hold on. - Hold my hand.

32:53.210 --> 32:54.420
跟在这个人后面
Get behind there.

32:54.500 --> 32:56.620
关上大门！
Close the gate!

32:56.710 --> 32:58.330
不准进了
No more through.

33:01.210 --> 33:03.750
- 不要 - 妈妈 不要
- No. - No. Mommy.

33:03.830 --> 33:06.620
- 维姬！求求开门啊！ - 不要啊 求您开门！
- Vicky! Please! - No, please, sir!

33:06.710 --> 33:09.080
- 开门啊！ - 关门！
- Open the gate! - Close the gate!

33:09.170 --> 33:11.000
- 开门！- 开开门啊！
- Open it! - Open the gate!

33:11.080 --> 33:14.870
- 后退 - 听着 去试试那扇门 走 快走
- Get back. - Look, try that one. Go. Go.

33:20.710 --> 33:22.790
大门现在已关闭！
The gates are locked now!

33:22.870 --> 33:24.210
打开！
Open!

33:24.290 --> 33:26.460
- 后退！- 开门啊！
- Get back! - Open the gate!

33:26.540 --> 33:29.250
军爷！军爷！
Soldier! Soldier!

33:29.330 --> 33:32.330
- 求求您开门吧！- 滚回家去！
- Please open the gate! - Go back to your homes!

33:32.420 --> 33:33.920
后退！门已经关上了！
Stay back! It's closed!

33:34.000 --> 33:35.420
当兵的！
Soldier!

33:36.920 --> 33:38.210
让开！别挤！
